sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethConvSummaryTable ('DataSetId' INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
'TotalConvergenceTime' FLOAT, 'MaxConvergenceTime' FLOAT, 'MinConvergenceTime' FLOAT, 'AverageConvergenceTime' FLOAT,
'EventTriggerDuration' FLOAT , 'FirstEventTriggerTime' FLOAT , 'LastEventTriggerTime' FLOAT,
'ExpectedStreamConvergenceCount' INTEGER, 'DetectedStreamPrimaryCount' INTEGER,
'StreamConvergenceCount' INTEGER, 'StreamExceededConvergenceThresholdCount' INTEGER,
'FirstStreamConvergenceTime' FLOAT, 'LastStreamConvergenceTime' FLOAT,
'FirstStreamLeaveTime' FLOAT, 'LastStreamLeaveTime' FLOAT)

SELECT DataSetId, TotConvTime AS 'TotalConvergenceTime', MaxConvTime AS 'MaxConvergenceTime', MinConvTime AS 'MinConvergenceTime', AvgConvTime AS 'AverageConvergenceTime', EventTrigDuration AS 'EventTriggerDuration', EventTrigMinTime AS 'FirstEventTriggerTime', EventTrigMaxTime AS 'LastEventTriggerTime', ExpConvStreams AS 'ExpectedStreamConvergenceCount', PrimaryStreams AS 'DetectedStreamPrimaryCount', ConvStreams AS 'StreamConvergenceCount', ExceededConvThreshStreams AS 'StreamExceededConvergenceThresholdCount', FirstConvStreamArrival AS 'FirstStreamConvergenceTime', LastConvStreamArrival AS 'LastStreamConvergenceTime', FirstStreamLeave AS 'FirstStreamLeaveTime', LastStreamLeave AS 'LastStreamLeaveTime' FROM (SELECT MAX(EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId) As DataSetId, MAX(FirstArrivalTime) - MIN(EventTimeStamp) As TotConvTime, MAX(FirstArrivalTime - EventTimeStamp) AS MaxConvTime, MIN(FirstArrivalTime - EventTimeStamp) AS MinConvTime, AVG(FirstArrivalTime - EventTimeStamp) AS AvgConvTime, MIN(FirstArrivalTime) AS FirstConvStreamArrival, MAX(FirstArrivalTime) AS LastConvStreamArrival FROM EotProtoEventResults INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults ON EventStreamId = Comp32 WHERE NOT EventDetail GLOB '*(T1)' AND ',' || AdditionalEventData || ',' GLOB '*,' || RxEotStreamResults.ParentHnd || ',*' AND FirstArrivalTime > 0.0 AND RxEotStreamResults.DataSetId = EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId) JOIN (SELECT COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT EventStreamId) FROM EotProtoEventResults), 0) AS ExpConvStreams, COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT EventStreamId) FROM EotProtoEventResults INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults ON EventStreamId = Comp32 AND RxEotStreamResults.ParentHnd = EotProtoEventResults.ParentHnd AND FirstArrivalTime > 0.0 AND RxEotStreamResults.DataSetId = EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId), 0) AS PrimaryStreams, COALESCE((SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT EventStreamId) FROM EotProtoEventResults INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults ON EventStreamId = Comp32 AND ',' || AdditionalEventData || ',' GLOB '*,' || RxEotStreamResults.ParentHnd || ',*' AND FirstArrivalTime > 0.0 AND RxEotStreamResults.DataSetId = EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId), 0) AS ConvStreams, MAX(EventTimeStamp) - MIN(EventTimeStamp) AS EventTrigDuration, MIN(EventTimeStamp) AS EventTrigMinTime, MAX(EventTimeStamp) AS EventTrigMaxTime FROM EotProtoEventResults) JOIN (SELECT MIN(LastArrivalTime) AS FirstStreamLeave, MAX(LastArrivalTime) AS LastStreamLeave FROM EotProtoEventResults INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults ON EventStreamId = Comp32 AND RxEotStreamResults.ParentHnd = EotProtoEventResults.ParentHnd AND FirstArrivalTime > 0.0 AND RxEotStreamResults.DataSetId = EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId) JOIN (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(EventStreamId)) As ExceededConvThreshStreams FROM EotProtoEventResults LEFT JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS Prim ON Prim.DataSetId = EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId AND EventStreamId = Prim.Comp32 AND Prim.ParentHnd = EotProtoEventResults.ParentHnd AND Prim.FirstArrivalTime > 0.0 LEFT JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS Back ON Back.DataSetId = EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId AND EventStreamId = Back.Comp32 AND ','||AdditionalEventData||',' GLOB '*,'||Back.ParentHnd||',*' WHERE (Back.FirstArrivalTime - EventTimeStamp) > (SELECT StreamConvergenceThreshold FROM ConvergenceConfig WHERE Handle == ParentConfigHandle))

SELECT TotalConvergenceTime AS 'Total Convergence Time (us)', MaxConvergenceTime AS 'Max Convergence Time (us)', MinConvergenceTime AS 'Min Convergence Time (us)', AverageConvergenceTime AS 'Avg Convergence Time (us)', EventTriggerDuration AS 'Event Trigger Duration (us)', FirstEventTriggerTime AS 'First Event Trigger Time (us)', LastEventTriggerTime AS 'Last Event Trigger Time (us)', ExpectedStreamConvergenceCount AS 'Number of Streams Expected To Converge', DetectedStreamPrimaryCount AS 'Number of Streams Detected On Primary', StreamConvergenceCount AS 'Number of Streams Converged', StreamExceededConvergenceThresholdCount AS 'Number of Streams Converged Exceeding Threshold', FirstStreamConvergenceTime AS 'First Stream Convergence Time (us)', LastStreamConvergenceTime AS 'Last Stream Convergence Time (us)' FROM MethConvSummaryTable

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END FROM MethConvSummaryTable

sql_statement.static: SELECT StreamConvergenceCount AS 'Number of Streams Converged', TotalConvergenceTime AS 'Total Convergence Time (us)' FROM MethConvSummaryTable

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: One or more streams failed to converge.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN "SELECT ExpectedStreamConvergenceCount, StreamConvergenceCount from MethConvSummaryTable where ExpectedStreamConvergenceCount == DetectedStreamPrimaryCount" > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethPrimaryStreamTimeTable ('Stream ID' INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
'Stream Index' INTEGER, 'Timestamp (us)' FLOAT, 'Stream Count' FLOAT)
SELECT -2 AS 'Stream ID', -2 AS 'Stream Index', MIN(FirstEventTriggerTime, FirstStreamLeaveTime) AS 'Timestamp (us)', SUM(DetectedStreamPrimaryCount) AS 'Stream Count' FROM MethConvSummaryTable
SELECT -1 AS 'Stream ID', -1 AS 'Stream Index', MIN(FirstStreamLeaveTime) AS 'Timestamp (us)', SUM(DetectedStreamPrimaryCount) AS 'Stream Count' FROM MethConvSummaryTable

Select S.Comp32 as 'Stream ID', S.'Stream Index' as 'Stream Index', S.LastArrivalTime as 'Timestamp (us)', COUNT(S.'Stream Index')-1 AS 'Stream Count' from (SELECT S.Comp32 as Comp32, S.StreamIndex as 'Stream Index', S.LastArrivalTime as LastArrivalTime FROM EotProtoEventResults INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults as S ON EventStreamId = Comp32 AND S.ParentHnd = EotProtoEventResults.ParentHnd AND FirstArrivalTime > 0.0) AS S, (SELECT S.StreamIndex as 'Stream Index', S.PortName as PortName, S.LastArrivalTime as LastArrivalTime FROM EotProtoEventResults INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults as S ON EventStreamId = Comp32 AND S.ParentHnd = EotProtoEventResults.ParentHnd AND FirstArrivalTime > 0.0) AS S2 Where S2.LastArrivalTime >= S.LastArrivalTime Group By S.Comp32 Order By S.LastArrivalTime

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Failed to create Primary Stream Table Summary.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END FROM MethPrimaryStreamTimeTable

sql_statement.static: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS MethSecondaryStreamTimeTable ('Stream ID' INTEGER PRIMARY KEY,
'Stream Index' INTEGER, 'Timestamp (us)' FLOAT, 'Stream Count' FLOAT)
SELECT -2 AS 'Stream ID', -1 AS 'Stream Index', MIN(FirstEventTriggerTime) AS 'Timestamp (us)', 0 AS 'Stream Count' FROM MethConvSummaryTable
SELECT -1 AS 'Stream ID', -1 AS 'Stream Index', MIN(FirstStreamConvergenceTime) AS 'Timestamp (us)', 0 AS 'Stream Count' FROM MethConvSummaryTable

Select S.Comp32 as 'Stream ID', S.'Stream Index' as 'Stream Index', S.FirstArrivalTime as 'Timestamp (us)', COUNT(S.'Stream Index') as 'Stream Count' FROM (SELECT S.Comp32 as Comp32, S.StreamIndex as 'Stream Index', S.FirstArrivalTime as FirstArrivalTime FROM EotProtoEventResults INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults as S ON EventStreamId = Comp32 AND ','||AdditionalEventData||',' GLOB '*,'||S.ParentHnd||',*' AND FirstArrivalTime > 0.0 AND S.DataSetId = EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId) AS S, (SELECT S.StreamIndex as 'Stream Index', S.PortName as PortName, S.FirstArrivalTime as FirstArrivalTime FROM EotProtoEventResults INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults as S ON EventStreamId = Comp32 AND ','||AdditionalEventData||',' GLOB '*,'||S.ParentHnd||',*' AND FirstArrivalTime > 0.0 AND S.DataSetId = EotProtoEventResults.DataSetId) AS S2 Where S2.FirstArrivalTime <= S.FirstArrivalTime Group By S.Comp32 Order By S.FirstArrivalTime

report_verdict.failed_verdict_explanation: Failed to create Secondary Stream Table Summary.

sql_for_verdict.static: SELECT CASE WHEN COUNT(*) > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END FROM MethSecondaryStreamTimeTable

sql_statement.static: SELECT MIN(FirstEventTriggerTime) AS Timestamp FROM MethConvSummaryTable
SELECT MIN(FirstEventTriggerTime) AS Timestamp FROM MethConvSummaryTable
SELECT MAX(LastEventTriggerTime) AS Timestamp FROM MethConvSummaryTable
SELECT MIN(FirstStreamConvergenceTime) AS Timestamp FROM MethConvSummaryTable
SELECT MAX(LastStreamConvergenceTime) AS Timestamp FROM MethConvSummaryTable

Properties.Name: Series
Value: SELECT "Timestamp (us)", "Stream Count" from MethPrimaryStreamTimeTable ORDER BY "Timestamp (us)"
SELECT "Timestamp (us)", "Stream Count" from MethSecondaryStreamTimeTable ORDER BY "Timestamp (us)"
